- Da. domnule.

249
00:37:09.125 --> 00:37:10.083
Stai aici.

250
00:37:48.500 --> 00:37:50.333
Ce e?

251
00:37:50.416 --> 00:37:51.666
E suficient.

252
00:37:56.166 --> 00:37:58.125
