269
00:40:03.791 --> 00:40:05.083
Eati foarte frumoasa.

270
00:40:08.125 --> 00:40:09.208
Mulaumesc.

271
00:40:10.750 --> 00:40:11.833
Cu placere.

272
00:40:14.958 --> 00:40:16.791
- Vrei sa intri?
- Da.

273
