anaeleg daca nu vrei s-o faci.
dar. daca iese bine. totul se va schimba.

282
00:42:30.375 --> 00:42:31.416
ai daca iese rau?

283
00:42:32.208 --> 00:42:34.666
Tu vei fi singurul responsabil.

284
00:42:36.541 --> 00:42:37.791
Suna bine.

285
00:44:19.500 --> 00:44:20.583
Ai auzit?

286
