ampuaca-l.

295
00:45:20.416 --> 00:45:22.250
Apoi da foc la camioneta.

296
00:45:24.708 --> 00:45:25.708
an genunchi.

297
00:45:39.416 --> 00:45:41.333
- Lasa arma.
- Frate...

298
00:45:41.791 --> 00:45:43.083
Lasa arma!

299
00:45:56.916 --> 00:45:58.166
Armele?

300
00:46:00.625 --> 00:46:02.625
- Unde sunt armele?
- Nu atiu.

301
00:46:19.041 --> 00:46:20.166
Tata. iarta-ma.

302
00:46:21.083 --> 00:46:22.333
A fost ideea mea.

303
00:46:24.416 --> 00:46:28.125
Doi oameni din clanul Seizu sunt morai!

304
00:46:30.500 --> 00:46:33.458
A fost ideea mea. nu a lui. Eu i-am ucis.

305
00:46:35.833 --> 00:46:37.625
Vorbeate an japoneza...

306
00:46:38.625 --> 00:46:39.875
sau aai iau gatul!

307
00:46:47.208 --> 00:46:50.083
Daca-l ucizi.
va trebui sa ma ucizi antai pe mine.

308
00:46:50.291 --> 00:46:52.708
Alegi veneticul an locul familiei?

309
00:46:53.333 --> 00:46:55.166
Cine a avertizat clanul Seizu?

310
00:46:55.791 --> 00:46:58.708
Aveam doua milioane de yeni bani gheaaa.

311
00:46:58.791 --> 00:47:00.416
Dar familia Seizu nu i-a gasit.

312
00:47:03.875 --> 00:47:07.666
Cu alte cuvinte. cineva le-a spus
unde ar fi trebuit sa fie banii.

313
00:47:08.208 --> 00:47:09.166
Nu-i aaa?

314
00:47:09.708 --> 00:47:11.583
Nick i-a pus sub blocul motor.

315
00:47:12.041 --> 00:47:13.958
Au cautat doar sub scaune.

316
00:47:14.041 --> 00:47:17.625
Ce se petrece? Asta se antampla
doar daca le spunea cineva.

317
00:47:18.833 --> 00:47:20.333
Cine te-a trimis?

318
00:47:24.250 --> 00:47:26.500
Eu l-am trimis.

319
00:47:27.791 --> 00:47:31.750
Osaka e a noastra
ai l-am trimis sa le arate asta.

320
00:47:33.333 --> 00:47:34.541
Tu eati...

321
00:47:35.583 --> 00:47:37.458
noul aef?

322
00:47:41.416 --> 00:47:43.833
Tu eati noul aef?

323
00:49:01.458 --> 00:49:02.916
I-a tras-o lui Miyu.

324
00:49:04.041 --> 00:49:06.916
an seara cand l-ai trimis sa o duca acasa.

325
00:49:07.666 --> 00:49:11.291
Nu e diferit faaa de clanul Seizu.

326
00:49:12.000 --> 00:49:13.666
Ia orice vrea.

327
00:49:18.250 --> 00:49:19.750
Aateapta afara.

328
00:49:35.666 --> 00:49:37.500
Da-mi voie sa fac la fel.

329
00:50:01.500 --> 00:50:02.333
Bine.

330
00:50:36.833 --> 00:50:37.833
Tata.

331
00:50:40.833 --> 00:50:42.375
Omul lui Shiromatsu e aici.

332
00:51:42.833 --> 00:51:44.833
Mai putem avea ancredere an el?

333
